    "asOf": "2023-02-16",
    "date": "2023-03-10T18:27:15Z",
    "text": "Codification of Verified Values Act or the CVV Act\n\nThis bill requires a contributor to political organizations who uses a credit card to make online contributions to such organizations to disclose the credit verification value of such credit card at the time a contribution is made. A credit verification value is a series of numbers on a credit card (usually on the back of the card) that provides additional security for a transaction by credit card."
